      "label": "Accepted for extraction",
      "meaning": "Evidence is relevant, within scope, attributable to entity/facility/period, and contains fields needed for extraction.",
      "product_action": "Send to extraction pipeline; link evidence to disclosure/source/category; preserve ISSA assertion tags."
